            <p class="text-white/95 text-base leading-relaxed">Affluent traveler researching "luxury safari private guide" visits 12 travel agency websites. 8 have stock photos only, no itinerary details, vague pricing, difficult consultation process. 1 modern site with stunning destination photography, detailed day-by-day itineraries, transparent luxury pricing, easy expert consultation booking. Guess who gets the $25,000 booking? For luxury travel, visible experience = dream trip = book now. Your website = 24/7 travel consultant that never sleeps.</p>
          </div>
