            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">November 2023: Migrated to Squarespace with Travel template. Added "Sample Itineraries" section with FULL day-by-day details: "Day 1: Private guide meets you at Kilimanjaru Airport, transfer to Four Seasons Safari Lodge, sunset game drive with champagne." Added REAL guest photo gallery (Instagram feeds from clients). Added "Meet Your Guides" section with expertise bios. Added transparent pricing: "10-Day Luxury Safari from $18,000/person including private guide, internal flights, luxury lodges."</p>
